class Solution {
    public int[][] generateMatrix(int n) {
        int[][] res = new int[n][n];

        // 循环次数
        int loop = n / 2;

        // 定义每次循环起始位置
        int startX = 0;
        int startY = 0;

        // 定义偏移量
        int offset = 1;

        // 定义填充数字
        int count = 1;

        // 定义中间位置
        int mid = n / 2;
        while (loop > 0) {
            int i = startX;
            int j = startY;

            // 模拟上侧从左到右
            for (; j<startY + n -offset; ++j) {
                res[startX][j] = count++;
            }

            // 模拟右侧从上到下
            for (; i<startX + n -offset; ++i) {
                res[i][j] = count++;
            }

            // 模拟下侧从右到左
            for (; j > startY; j--) {
                res[i][j] = count++;
            }

            // 模拟左侧从下到上
            for (; i > startX; i--) {
                res[i][j] = count++;
            }

            loop--;

            startX += 1;
            startY += 1;

            offset += 2;
        }

        if (n % 2 == 1) {
            res[mid][mid] = count;
        }

        return res;
    }
}
